These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, cola
Movie-Genre: horror, adventure
Sport: snowboarding, tennis
Transport: quad-bike, airplane
1. Transport:airplane is on the left or right of Sport:tennis##3
2. Beverage:cola is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:adventure == Beverage:7up##1
4. Transport:airplane is on the right of Transport:quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up  | cola   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | horror   |
| Sport         | tennis | snowboarding |
| Transport     | quad-bike | airplane    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: peach, carrot
Movie-Genre: scientific, zombie
Pet: bird, pony
Transport: ship, helicopter
1. Pet:pony is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:scientific == Transport:helicopter##1
3. Food:carrot is on the right of Movie-Genre:zombie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | peach     | carrot |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | scientific  |
| Pet           | pony         | bird     |
| Transport     | ship   | helicopter    |

 #################################
 
